568
00:32:08,715 --> 00:32:09,354
Exactly.

569
00:32:09,635 --> 00:32:11,314
Ms. Li is almost at her limit too.

570
00:32:12,114 --> 00:32:13,114
At dinner,

571
00:32:13,635 --> 00:32:14,715
