572
00:32:14,834 --> 00:32:15,395
Right?

573
00:32:15,675 --> 00:32:16,175
Yes.

574
00:32:16,235 --> 00:32:17,155
So, can you handle it?

575
00:32:17,435 --> 00:32:18,754
Me? I can handle it.

576
00:32:18,834 --> 00:32:19,594
Can you handle it?

577
00:32:20,834 --> 00:32:21,915
M-Master,

578
00:32:22,235 --> 00:32:23,395
