and we haven't even seen anyone.

585
00:32:38,235 --> 00:32:39,754
I understand.

586
00:32:40,915 --> 00:32:42,834
This situation really

587
00:32:43,235 --> 00:32:45,034
is disrupting everyone's regular work,

588
00:32:45,074 --> 00:32:46,594
and more importantly, your health.

589
00:32:46,834 --> 00:32:47,715
It's truly not right.

590
00:32:47,915 --> 00:32:49,514
So how about this?

591
00:32:49,955 --> 00:32:52,754
From now on, everyone focus
on your own tasks.

592
00:32:52,834 --> 00:32:56,034
I'll keep the city inspectors going
for a few more days.

593
00:32:56,195 --> 00:32:58,715
And I'll discuss with Chief Tian,

594
00:32:59,034 --> 00:33:00,995
