596
00:33:03,435 --> 00:33:04,915
Take care of yourself too, Mr. Tan.

597
00:33:05,435 --> 00:33:06,436
Apply to the higher-ups.

598
00:33:07,314 --> 00:33:08,635
Mr. Zheng, what do you think?

599
00:33:10,114 --> 00:33:11,274
Mr. Zheng? Mr. Zheng!

600
00:33:12,235 --> 00:33:12,955
What's wrong?

601
00:33:13,235 --> 00:33:14,034
- Mr. Zheng!
- Mr. Zheng!

602
00:33:14,034 --> 00:33:14,715
- What's wrong?
- What's wrong?

603
00:33:17,114 --> 00:33:17,955
