606
00:33:49,875 --> 00:33:51,955
There really is a situation.
Quick, notify them!

607
00:33:53,195 --> 00:33:55,955
Situation on the suburban road
west pass. Requesting backup.

608
00:33:56,915 --> 00:33:57,754
West pass?

609
00:33:57,955 --> 00:33:58,594
Yes, west exit.

610
00:34:07,395 --> 00:34:08,475
Fan,

611
00:34:09,194 --> 00:34:09,875
