612
00:34:10,034 --> 00:34:11,154
We must stay calm right now.

613
00:34:11,315 --> 00:34:12,995
Let's observe for a moment, okay?

614
00:34:14,795 --> 00:34:15,714
Mr. Tan, flashlight.

615
00:34:16,915 --> 00:34:17,475
Turn it off.

616
00:34:17,795 --> 00:34:18,435
Off.

617
