628
00:34:44,435 --> 00:34:44,995
Sir.

629
00:34:48,074 --> 00:34:48,920
Quick, they're here!

630
00:34:49,435 --> 00:34:49,935
Go!

631
00:34:51,714 --> 00:34:52,875
Stop! Don't move!

632
00:34:52,875 --> 00:34:53,554
Stop!

633
00:34:55,915 --> 00:34:56,714
Just two people.

634
00:34:59,355 --> 00:34:59,855
Well...

635
00:35:00,634 --> 00:35:01,355
What do you want?

636
00:35:02,074 --> 00:35:03,234
Don't you dare act rashly!

637
00:35:03,514 --> 00:35:06,514
I'm warning you.
You've broken the law, you understand?

638
00:35:09,475 --> 00:35:12,114
Fan! What are you doing?

639
00:35:12,435 --> 00:35:14,154
Y-You have no respect for the law!

640
00:35:14,355 --> 00:35:15,915
I'm the deputy mayor of Yuehai Town.

641
00:35:16,114 --> 00:35:18,194
I've already notified Chief Tian.
Do you know him?

642
00:35:18,275 --> 00:35:19,654
You... Hello?

643
00:35:22,355 --> 00:35:23,554
You dare take off your mask?

644
00:35:23,634 --> 00:35:25,154
I want to see who you really are!

645
00:35:46,795 --> 00:35:49,034
What are you waiting for?
Get the goods loaded!

646
00:35:56,915 --> 00:35:57,514
In the truck!

647
00:35:58,315 --> 00:35:58,835
Get in!

648
00:36:19,954 --> 00:36:25,355
(Pingchuan County)

649
00:36:25,355 --> 00:36:25,855
Tan.

650
00:36:26,194 --> 00:36:26,755
Mr. Zheng.

651
00:36:27,154 --> 00:36:27,755
You're awake.

652
00:36:28,275 --> 00:36:28,915
- Mr. Zheng.
- You're awake.

653
00:36:29,034 --> 00:36:29,835
No, don't move.

654
00:36:29,915 --> 00:36:30,475
No, Mr. Zheng.

655
00:36:30,514 --> 00:36:31,795
The doctor said don't move.

656
00:36:32,034 --> 00:36:33,415
The doctor said so. Be good.

657
00:36:33,795 --> 00:36:34,295
Got it?

658
00:36:34,634 --> 00:36:35,714
Mr. Zheng, listen...

659
00:36:35,714 --> 00:36:36,395
I know.

660
00:36:36,835 --> 00:36:38,275
If I catch that rat,

661
00:36:38,594 --> 00:36:40,034
I'll beat him to death!

662
00:36:40,795 --> 00:36:41,915
Don't worry.

663
00:36:41,955 --> 00:36:44,355
Mr. Tan, thank goodness.
You're finally awake.

664
00:36:44,435 --> 00:36:44,935
Chief Tian.

665
00:36:45,634 --> 00:36:46,234
Talk later.

666
00:36:46,395 --> 00:36:48,514
No, he just woke up!

667
00:36:48,714 --> 00:36:50,475
- Cut us some slack.
- He just woke up!

668
00:36:50,475 --> 00:36:53,594
There's only two of us. We need
to hurry, or the suspects will get away.

669
00:36:54,835 --> 00:36:55,835
Tell us the specifics.

670
00:36:57,514 --> 00:36:58,034
Lie down.

671
00:36:58,634 --> 00:36:59,275
Lie down!

672
00:36:59,594 --> 00:37:00,835
Please lie down.

673
00:37:01,194 --> 00:37:01,835
Take your time.

674
00:37:05,315 --> 00:37:06,995
La-Last night,

675
00:37:08,234 --> 00:37:09,514
there were

676
00:37:11,435 --> 00:37:12,154
six...

677
00:37:15,034 --> 00:37:16,674
It was pitch black.

678
00:37:17,395 --> 00:37:19,634
And honestly, we were panicking.

679
00:37:19,955 --> 00:37:22,875
Don't rush. Say whatever comes to mind.

680
00:37:24,094 --> 00:37:26,194
Anyway, there were at least five people.

681
00:37:27,955 --> 00:37:30,475
And two trucks.

682
00:37:31,074 --> 00:37:31,674
Small trucks?

683
00:37:32,955 --> 00:37:33,875
They drove trucks?

684
00:37:35,755 --> 00:37:36,408
Anything else?

685
00:37:39,395 --> 00:37:40,074
They

686
00:37:41,634 --> 00:37:44,355
were all wearing these plastic masks.

687
00:37:45,674 --> 00:37:47,074
Wh-What kind of masks?

688
00:37:48,395 --> 00:37:50,114
All sorts of masks.

689
00:37:51,275 --> 00:37:52,915
But I remember there was

690
00:37:53,835 --> 00:37:54,435
a Guan Yu.

691
00:37:55,315 --> 00:37:56,395
Guan Yu?

692
00:37:59,634 --> 00:38:00,955
Guan Yu is easy to spot.

693
00:38:02,594 --> 00:38:03,154
What else?

694
00:38:04,074 --> 00:38:05,514
And well,

695
00:38:07,875 --> 00:38:08,674
their clothes

696
00:38:09,234 --> 00:38:10,755
were pretty ordinary.

697
00:38:11,714 --> 00:38:12,440
Here's the thing.

698
00:38:12,714 --> 00:38:15,594
The previous victims
were all knocked out from behind.

699
00:38:16,154 --> 00:38:18,154
Mr. Tan, you're the only one
who saw them.

700
00:38:19,554 --> 00:38:21,194
Think hard. What else can you remember?

701
00:38:23,315 --> 00:38:25,514
What are you waiting for?
Get the goods loaded!

702
00:38:25,714 --> 00:38:26,214
Get in!

703
00:38:33,955 --> 00:38:34,755
That's all.

704
00:38:37,034 --> 00:38:37,534
Alright.

705
00:38:38,114 --> 00:38:39,275
Mr. Tan, rest well.

706
00:38:39,634 --> 00:38:40,475
We'll go investigate.

707
00:38:40,795 --> 00:38:41,395
Thanks, Chief.

708
00:38:41,395 --> 00:38:41,995
We're leaving.

709
00:38:41,995 --> 00:38:42,995
Thank you.

710
00:38:46,614 --> 00:38:47,114
Mr. Zheng.

711
00:38:47,114 --> 00:38:47,674
Don't move!

712
00:38:47,755 --> 00:38:49,714
The doctor said
the wound'll reopen if you get up.

713
00:38:50,514 --> 00:38:52,214
Alright, I'll support your head.

714
00:38:52,395 --> 00:38:53,034
Okay.

715
00:38:53,395 --> 00:38:54,234
Well... Mr. Zheng,

716
00:38:55,835 --> 00:38:59,234
