I didn't tell Chief Tian just now.

717
00:39:00,275 --> 00:39:00,875
What is it?

718
00:39:02,074 --> 00:39:05,435
It's about that Guan Yu...

719
00:39:05,835 --> 00:39:06,475
What about him?

720
00:39:07,275 --> 00:39:08,995
Well, it's possible

721
00:39:09,234 --> 00:39:11,995
that I was too nervous

722
00:39:12,395 --> 00:39:14,995
