723
00:39:15,475 --> 00:39:16,034
But...

724
00:39:16,634 --> 00:39:19,355
Stop beating around the bush!
Spit it out!

725
00:39:21,114 --> 00:39:23,475
That Guan Yu's voice

726
00:39:24,234 --> 00:39:25,674
