727
00:39:26,835 --> 00:39:27,395
Who?

728
00:39:29,835 --> 00:39:30,435
Zhiqiang.

729
00:39:40,514 --> 00:39:42,554
This dish really goes well with rice.

730
00:39:42,674 --> 00:39:43,995
It goes well with rice.

731
00:39:45,194 --> 00:39:46,114
If you like it, I'll...

732
00:39:46,114 --> 00:39:48,455
Having dinner?

733
00:39:48,534 --> 00:39:49,034
You're here.

734
00:39:49,034 --> 00:39:49,955
- Stay for dinner.
- We're just eating.

735
00:39:49,955 --> 00:39:50,714
No, I've eaten.

736
00:39:50,915 --> 00:39:53,315
I need Zhiqiang for something.
Come here.

737
00:39:54,435 --> 00:39:55,034
What is it?

738
00:39:59,514 --> 00:40:01,234
Did Decheng find Zhiqiang a job?

739
00:40:01,875 --> 00:40:02,634
Probably.

740
00:40:10,955 --> 00:40:12,114
- Why draw the curtain?
- What happened?

741
00:40:12,395 --> 00:40:12,895
No idea.

742
00:40:18,634 --> 00:40:19,755
What are you looking for?

743
00:40:29,634 --> 00:40:30,134
Uncle.

744
00:40:40,875 --> 00:40:42,554
Uncle, what are you looking for?

745
00:40:45,234 --> 00:40:45,795
Uncle.

746
00:41:00,714 --> 00:41:01,755
Where were you last night?

747
00:41:04,475 --> 00:41:05,674
I was at home.

748
00:41:06,875 --> 00:41:07,514
Be honest.

749
00:41:11,234 --> 00:41:12,594
Uncle, what are you implying?

750
00:41:12,714 --> 00:41:13,674
What am I implying?

751
00:41:14,835 --> 00:41:16,234
