756
00:41:27,194 --> 00:41:27,955
I want the truth.

757
00:41:29,315 --> 00:41:30,714
Where were you last night?

758
00:41:32,875 --> 00:41:35,234
Uncle, you don't really think
I did it, do you?

759
00:41:35,594 --> 00:41:36,795
How would I dare?

760
00:41:37,475 --> 00:41:39,154
I really was home last night.

761
00:41:42,514 --> 00:41:43,114
Decheng,

762
00:41:45,714 --> 00:41:46,915
Zhiqiang isn't lying.

763
00:41:47,955 --> 00:41:49,514
He was home last night.

764
00:42:00,755 --> 00:42:01,315
Desheng,

765
00:42:02,795 --> 00:42:03,554
are you sure

766
00:42:04,714 --> 00:42:07,634
