and didn't go out?

767
00:42:22,114 --> 00:42:24,435
Desheng, let me be honest with you.

768
00:42:25,234 --> 00:42:26,315
This is serious.

769
00:42:27,275 --> 00:42:28,315
There are a lot

770
00:42:28,795 --> 00:42:30,154
